CustomField.description: If Checked, user will be allowed to edit FedEx Commercial Invoice records that have already been used in a Shipment. Any changes made will no longer reflect the data submitted to FedEx with the existing shipments.

CustomField.label: Allow Edit of Used Commercial Invoices
